WEBVTT

00:01.450 --> 00:04.051
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:05.154 --> 00:06.921
Hi, Miss Howe.

00:06.923 --> 00:08.156
Hi, Kelly.

00:08.157 --> 00:11.376
This... is for you.

00:11.410 --> 00:13.411
For me?

00:13.445 --> 00:15.279
What is it?

00:15.280 --> 00:16.314
(gasps)

00:16.315 --> 00:19.751
Oh, Kelly, this is beautiful.

00:19.785 --> 00:21.169
Why me?

00:21.203 --> 00:24.405
Because I like you and you've
always shown me friendship.

00:24.406 --> 00:25.508
Well, that's sweet, Kelly.

00:25.509 --> 00:27.175
Thank you.

00:27.209 --> 00:29.678
And I want you to keep
your hands off my man.

00:32.265 --> 00:34.049
Do we understand each other?

00:34.100 --> 00:36.283
Not really.
(laughs)

00:36.352 --> 00:38.119
Don't play dumb with me,
Miss Howe.

00:38.154 --> 00:39.454
I invented it.

00:40.940 --> 00:43.775
You know, Woody tells me
how you look at him.

00:43.777 --> 00:45.126
Kelly, I don't look at him.

00:45.161 --> 00:46.528
I know you do, Miss Howe,

00:46.530 --> 00:50.081
and I'm prepared to buy you
one of these every month

00:50.116 --> 00:52.750
if you keep away from my Woody.

00:55.621 --> 00:58.957
Well, you know, Kelly,
he is awfully cute.

00:58.991 --> 01:00.358
All right, one a week.

01:00.392 --> 01:02.594
Do we have a deal?
Deal.

01:04.797 --> 01:08.015
Do you know where Carla is?

01:08.101 --> 01:09.868
(theme song begins)

01:14.006 --> 01:16.324
♪ Making your way
in the world today ♪

01:16.359 --> 01:19.544
♪ Takes everything you've got ♪

01:19.579 --> 01:22.213
♪ Taking a break
from all your worries ♪

01:22.247 --> 01:25.684
♪ Sure would help a lot ♪

01:25.718 --> 01:29.554
♪ Wouldn't you like
to get away? ♪

01:30.823 --> 01:33.125
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:33.159 --> 01:37.612
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:38.914 --> 01:43.551
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:43.586 --> 01:45.820
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:45.854 --> 01:48.389
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:48.423 --> 01:52.661
♪ You wanna be where
everybody knows your name ♪

01:53.896 --> 01:55.863
♪ You wanna go
where people know ♪

01:55.898 --> 01:59.100
♪ People are all the same ♪

01:59.134 --> 02:03.705
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

